---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="Denver Preschool Program Case Study | Upfront" description="See how Denver Preschool Program partnered with Upfront to streamline tuition credits and help Denver families afford quality preschool.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-teal hover:text-brand-teal/80 transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        Back to Case Studies
      </a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
        <img
          src="/images/partners/denver-preschool-program.png"
          alt="Denver Preschool Program logo"
          class="h-16 w-auto"
        />
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
        Denver Preschool Program
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-gray">
        Streamlining Tuition Credits for Denver Families
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Challenge -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-orange uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        The Challenge
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        The Problem
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        Denver Preschool Program (DPP) provides tuition credits to help Denver families afford quality preschool. However, the existing processes created friction for families, providers, and staff alike:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Paper-heavy applications: families navigated confusing forms and waited weeks for processing</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Provider burden: preschools managed enrollment and billing through disconnected spreadsheets</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Limited search: families couldn't easily find DPP-participating providers with openings</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Reporting challenges: staff compiled funding reports manually each month</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Solution -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        The Solution
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        A Modern Platform for Tuition Credits
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-8">
        Upfront partnered with DPP to build an integrated system that simplifies the entire tuition credit process for families, providers, and staff.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Family Search Portal</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Find DPP providers by location, schedule, and availability with an intuitive search experience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Online Applications</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Families apply in minutes with instant eligibility determination, replacing weeks of paper processing.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Provider Portal</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Manage enrollment, attendance, and billing in one place, eliminating disconnected spreadsheets.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Automated Payments</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Tuition credits processed monthly without manual intervention, ensuring providers get paid on time.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Real-time Dashboards</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Track enrollment, spending, and capacity across the city with automated reporting.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Results -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
          The Results
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
          Transforming Preschool Access in Denver
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Upfront's platform has streamlined the tuition credit process, making quality preschool more accessible to Denver families.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">40%</div>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-navy font-medium">
            faster application processing
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">300+</div>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-navy font-medium">
            participating providers
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">95%</div>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-navy font-medium">
            provider portal adoption
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner />
</Layout>
